# CardItem

`TxCardItem` is a compact row primitive for settings pages, command lists, and lightweight navigation. It renders optional media on the left, title/subtitle/description text in the middle, and a right-side action slot while keeping interactivity opt-in through `clickable`.

## Basic Usage

Use the `right` slot for switches, chevrons, metadata, or secondary status. The row itself does not emit clicks unless `clickable` is enabled.

